automatic setup for branchmana und githookinstaller
VituviusGitIntegration.setupProject(projectPath) {
    1. Install all Git hooks (post-checkout, pre-commit, pre-merge, ...)
    2. Create .vitruvius directory structure
    3. Start all watchers (reload, validation, ...)
    4. Configure handlers
    5. Verify Git repository exists
    6. Maybe: add .gitignore for trigger files
    7. Maybe: configure hook behavior
}

